{
  "stem": "8212.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was mostly topinambur, which is some kind of potatoes, and rutabaga, which is the kind of thing they give to their cows to eat, like-- what is that?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Navet in French, rutabaga.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not like carrots.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's-- I don't know how to call it in English.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it's carrot-like, but that kind of a vegetable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But really, the French only gave it to their animals.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's what we ate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So my mother at this point-- there was a little town right next to it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you-- you could go out during the day with a permission-- out and come back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It wasn't a-- how do you call it?-- a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a camp where they kept those families.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So my mother had a wonderful idea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She started-- she was always very good with sewing, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She crocheted little napperons, little-- very nice little things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had very little money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But she went to the people, to the bakers, to the charcutiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she got food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She exchanged it against food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She explained that we were in that camp, and then she put the food like under her dress, and-- when she went back.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we always had something extra to eat, a little extra bread, a little extra pate, a little-- whatever she got.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She-- she was very creative in this sense, so we were not really hungry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then slowly, in that camp, where we were just for a few months-- and funnily enough, in that camp, there were lots and lots of young people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we got together every afternoon, the young people, in that room where you ate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we sang Jewish songs and we danced the hora, and it was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was very uplifting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I loved it.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
